name: Another Cubing Game
description:
Pressing START will NOT erase any progress, it just takes you to level 1.
CONTINUE takes you to the last level you were on.

The same idea as "Tom's Cubing Game". This is the sequel, with a whole 'nother 20 levels of cubing-based riddles and puzzles.

If you aren't a cuber and you're here for some reason, none of it will make any sense.
